      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EYE KEEP SMILING (7) is gunning for her third straight win in this race and looks to be on target having resumed with a 1.2m second after working from this barrier last week. Yet to miss a place in five second-up attempts including two wins so should be improved. Her record at this circuit and distance stands at six from eight so can achieve the threepeat. STENO (5) worked and faded last week but had been ultra consistent with a string of wins and placings prior, scoring here two back. Has placed behind EYE KEEP SMILING at Group 1 level a couple of times including this race last year. Could turn the tables with her A-game. COOL AND CLASSY (8) returns to her own sex after working and finishing down the track in the Rising Sun. Won two in a row prior and her record at this circuit and distance stands at 11 from 14. BELLA DANZA (9) made it two in a row when beating EYE KEEP SMILING from this row last week. Hard to knock. RUBY RULES (6) has been racing consistently and is worth including.",
